{"tid":2501041,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"維多利亞城界石遊","createTime":"2021-04-23T05:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:24:06.000Z","uid":150807,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b979cae7da574a851136c8901f59139ce51be9b3","tid":2501041,"uid":150807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"今日時間緊張，無得出遠啲玩<br />\n不過市區都有條線幾特別<br />\n就係探下殖民地時留低既界石<br />\n<br />\n以下抄一抄綠洲既資料：<br />\n由維城東至西面，七座界石分別位於：<br />\n<br />\n一：跑馬地黃泥涌道（聖保祿天主教小學對面）<br />\n二：寶雲道（近寶雲道及司徒拔道交界；寶雲道健身徑起點）<br />\n三：馬己仙峽道17號 （已遺失）<br />\n四：舊山頂道（近舊山頂道及地利根德徑交界）<br />\n五：克頓道（近克頓道配水庫）<br />\n六：薄扶林道84號（近富林苑側行人隧道口）<br />\n七：西寧街堅尼地城臨時遊樂場（近遊樂場西面入口；西寧閣對面）<br />\n<br />\n無錯，界石真係隨時會被政府拆左，所以要及早記錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZVUmj7VUFu8nTVvnHXjjKfuyn2p3c7GqgjGvbXdtfhHn?filename=56eyUUv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56eyUUv.png&h=989302a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由加多近街出發，堅彌地城起步"},{"pid":"9cf0654affb7878a6f7e43bce80ff745096ca7eb","tid":2501041,"uid":371177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8c90b96e2ed62ffe3b5bca4f8cda680c4a19960f","tid":2501041,"uid":51446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"有冇睇 點對點？"},{"pid":"43569da9800f1bbc5bd9e66a76ac3d11fec06aea","tid":2501041,"uid":150807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPxt54ymRrWjjWerYzLriHLoruUoyRrRASh3bwuwhSk11?filename=bbunOg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbunOg9.jpg&h=25d82385&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZWks7EGVW2EAfF3acowzJCBCHgEWm7gkBKs8Lfk7Krdn?filename=3Zrxq3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Zrxq3V.jpg&h=a032c0cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話咁快到左，可以見到特區政府去殖化係做得幾好<br />\n睇得出佢唔想理舊界石"},{"pid":"552e